ic cure for the virus tomorrow, stocks will rally and all the new retail in=
vestors will happily sell into the rally at the top and go back to their ot=
her, more entertaining, entertainments.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin:=
 16px 0;">When I wrote that, I probably underestimated the ways in which tr=
